responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[24F282B6434E981D3FBC5B9E3C7849C5]", "90017F604FE2551587C60F8CE573002E", "When you\'re ready, we need all of our people joined up down the river at Bonfire - that\'s where we\'ve decided to gather. Still, the way there isn\'t easy. Malae Kelori was one of the first of us downstream, she\'s posted up midway down to make sure folks like you make it all the way there. Those, uh, nasty beasts I told you about, see. Get down there. She\'ll help you on to Bonfire.")
